    silver: 'The party holds Silver rank in the League of Adventurers. IF contracts are offered, they may involve dangerous regional threats, sensitive clients, faction complications, long-distance travel, difficult monsters, and operations tied to larger powers. They are established professionals. Disregard this instruction if no League contract is being offered or discussed.',
